Subject: [PATCH] use AM_MAINTAINER_MODE

so ./configure isn't being rerun during build
---
 configure.ac |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/configure.ac b/configure.ac
index 03f9388..a5fc7ee 100644
--- a/configure.ac
+++ b/configure.ac
@@ -21,6 +21,7 @@ AM_INIT_AUTOMAKE
 AC_CONFIG_MACRO_DIR([m4])
 
 AC_PROG_LIBTOOL
+AM_MAINTAINER_MODE
 
 dnl Check for basic C environment.
 AC_PROG_CC_STDC
